  <mainContent><![CDATA[<h2>Course Overview</h2>
<p>Drama &amp; Theatre Studies gives you the opportunity to explore the theory behind creating effective theatre and develop skills to enable you to create your own. During the course you will look at work in a variety of styles from the point of view of Director, Designer and Performer.</p>]]></mainContent>
